description:
Ed Boon join Chris Hayner to Mortal Kombat 1's upcoming Khaos Reigns DLC, and new guest fighters that include Scream's Ghostface, Terminator 2's T-1000, and Conan the Barbarian.

We even get Ed Boon's thoughts on Homelander's milking drinking animation.

#mortalkombat1 #gaming #sdcc
title: Mortal Kombat 1 - New Guest Fighters Discussion with Ed Boon | SDCC 2024
